#

Seared Steak with Garlic Butter

25 min
$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-freeHigh-protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickMeatDinner

Description

Juicy seared steak topped with rich garlic butter for a mouthwatering experience.

Ingredients

  • ribeye steak: 2 (8 oz each)
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • butter: 3 tablespoons
  • garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
